data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home! This cozy twin home is perfect for those who want a comfortable living space without the hassle of stairs. The kitchen comes equipped with a microwave and refrigerator purchased in Aug of 2023. The home features two bedrooms and a full bathroom, providing just enough space for a small family or anyone who desires a guest room or home office. Additionally, this home includes a private backyard, perfect for enjoying warm summer evenings. Don't miss out on the chance to make this lovely single-story small twin home your own!
